==== 合成 Compounding

- 闭合式：blackboard, bedroom
- 连字符：part-time, snow-white
- 开放式：coffee table, high school

==== 转类 Conversion / Zero-derivation

- 名词→动词：to Google, to email
- 动词→名词：a call, a run
- 形容词→名词：the poor, the elderly [the + 形容词：表示一类人]

==== 混成 Blending

- smoke + fog → smog
- breakfast + lunch → brunch
- web + seminar → webinar

==== 截短 Clipping 与逆生 Back-formation

- 截短：lab（laboratory）, ad（advertisement）, exam（examination）
- 逆生：editor → edit；option → opt

